&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fi Ultra works by using a combination of GPS, LTE, and Starlink satellite technology to track your dog&amp;rsquo;s location.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;what-are-the-key-features-of-fi-ultra&#34; class=&#34;heading &#34;&gt;What are the key features of Fi Ultra?&lt;a href=&#34;#what-are-the-key-features-of-fi-ultra&#34; aria-labelledby=&#34;what-are-the-key-features-of-fi-ultra&#34;&gt;
