&lt;h4 id=&#34;q-what-is-the-price-of-the-msi-katana-laptop&#34; class=&#34;heading &#34;&gt;Q: What is the price of the MSI Katana laptop?&lt;a href=&#34;#q-what-is-the-price-of-the-msi-katana-laptop&#34; aria-labelledby=&#34;q-what-is-the-price-of-the-msi-katana-laptop&#34;&gt;
