&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A: The MSI Katana laptop features a 15.6-inch 1440p display, Nvidia RTX 5060 GPU, Intel Core i7 14650HX CPU, 16GB DDR5 RAM, and a 1TB SSD.&lt;/p&gt;
