&lt;h3 id=&#34;future-of-gaming-laptops&#34; class=&#34;heading &#34;&gt;Future of Gaming Laptops&lt;a href=&#34;#future-of-gaming-laptops&#34; aria-labelledby=&#34;future-of-gaming-laptops&#34;&gt;
