&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information on the Google Pixel lineup and the potential price increase, readers can check out our previous articles on the topic. We have also written about the
&lt;a href=&#34;/posts/the-verges-guide-to-amazon-prime-day-2026/&#34;&gt;Prime Day 2026 Unveiled: A Tech Deep Dive&lt;/a&gt;, which includes information on the best deals and discounts available on the Google Pixel lineup and other devices. Additionally, readers can check out our article on
