&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here are some frequently asked questions about the Twelve South AirFly Pro:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;What is the AirFly Pro?
The AirFly Pro is a Bluetooth accessory designed to make traveling more convenient. It supports both Bluetooth transmitter and receiver modes, allowing you to stream audio from various devices to your headphones or speakers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;What devices is the AirFly Pro compatible with?
The AirFly Pro is compatible with a wide range of devices, including in-flight entertainment systems, older rental car stereos, Nintendo Switch, and gym equipment.&lt;/li&gt;
