The AirFly Pro has a battery life of up to 25 hours, ensuring that you can enjoy uninterrupted audio throughout your travels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Can I use the AirFly Pro with multiple headphones?
Yes, the AirFly Pro can connect to two pairs of Bluetooth headphones at once, making it ideal for sharing audio with a friend or family member.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
