&lt;p&gt;In conclusion, the Twelve South AirFly Pro is a great travel companion that&amp;rsquo;s now on sale for $40. Its convenience, versatility, long battery life, and compatibility make it an ideal accessory for use in various travel scenarios. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re flying, driving, or working out, the AirFly Pro is a great device to have in your travel kit. For more information on travel accessories and gadgets, you may want to check out our articles on
